title: C7V1
description:
The first Space Marine tech video detailing the range weaponry used by the super soldiers of the Imperium. This was going to include the close combat weaponry as well, but even I felt sleepy after all of that, so the next installment in the Space Marines series will be the Close combat Armory followed by the armor, vehicles and equipment videos, broken down into shorter, non sleep inducing videos. Glory be to Khorne... err the Emperor.
-
-
*Oops*
